{"tid":1236320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"向馬會攝記哥哥致意","createTime":"2019-06-17T11:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T13:21:06.000Z","uid":94824,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a4a3721d46816798fb7d69d9ba33cd792c1fbc","tid":1236320,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:43:25.000Z","msg":"多謝你係冇支援情況下咁勇敢守護言論自由<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢老仆街死；輸撚死你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20190617/59726135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F59726135&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=8d5c5596\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F59726135&h=e5e2422f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20190617/59726135</a>"},{"pid":"4561496a93e9e1bcbd80a2aab2be136a25d6d579","tid":1236320,"uid":94824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"要多啲人知"},{"pid":"0f8159ac9d72b71afa81206ec456ec2663b87753","tid":1236320,"uid":94824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"馬會今日（17日）發新聞稿指，就昨天（16日）一名馬會兼職攝影師在沙田馬場賽事期間，進行抗議一事的處理手法，該會保安及誠信審查總監蒲汝傑將向當事人致歉。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於當時部份馬迷對該示威人士的行動表達強烈不滿，保安人員對該並未影響賽事運作及人身安全的非暴力抗議，採取了不恰當的回應及處理。<br />\n<br />\n蒲汝傑總監將與該名兼職攝影師會面，親身表達歉意，並已提醒保安人員在處理示威時所需的敏感度。<br />\n<br />\n事緣昨日（16日）第九場五陵會鑽禧挑戰盃賽後頒獎期間，會員席突然出現馬會兼職攝影師舉起一個紙牌，上面寫着「反送中、撤惡法、不撤不散」的字眼，而他全程沒有叫口號，僅以和平方式向政府表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n在場的一眾保安，當時迅速搶去其紙牌，並以武力將他制服，把他撳在地上，而當事人當時曾說：「我只係舉牌，嗌都冇嗌過，點解要拉低我？」<br />\n<br />\n該兼職攝影師當時舉動，亦曾引起他站在他背後的馬迷大叔，向他以粗口謾罵。<br />\n<br />\n之後他留在現場繼續工作，其上司則被馬會高層召見以了解情況。"},{"pid":"0356c4cda14c5533e03aa8b6e81a8798daef3069","tid":1236320,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:57:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21dbf488c46412ef31f6813f677b7ca18ee4d10e","tid":1236320,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dd9d059365e63d30bcc66c3f30c6fa8cae707ff","tid":1236320,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"屌呢個真係好撚勇，一條友深入廢老重地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fe2f1d10e92f2d6044922dd3bffd7046ca85db","tid":1236320,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dd9d059365e63d30bcc66c3f30c6fa8cae707ff","tid":1236320,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"屌呢個真係好撚勇，一條友深入廢老重地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"唔係架，馬場成日有人噓特首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c38c5c81b4cfebe49e27471a64f307b2b604858","tid":1236320,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:21:06.000Z","msg":"今晚跑馬地有跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}